  <summary>5/1/2003--Introduced.
Montgomery GI Bill Flexibility Act of 2003 - Extends the period of entitlement to educational assistance under the Montgomery GI Bill to 14 (currently, ten) years after the date of an individual's last discharge or release from active duty.</summary>
